<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلَا بَأْسَ أَنْ يَخْطُبَ مِنْ صَحِيفَةٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَيَحْرُمُ الكَلَامُ وَالإِمَامُ يَخْطُبُ، وَهُوَ مِنْهُ بِحَيْثُ يَسْمَعُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُبَاحُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- إِذَا سَكَتَ بَيْنَهُمَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- أَوْ شَرَعَ فِي دُعَاءٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَالجُمُعَةُ رَكْعَتَانِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَحَرُمَ إِقامَتُهَا وَعِيدٍ فِي أَكْثرَ مِنْ مَوْضِعٍ مِنَ البَلَدِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> إِلَّا لِحَاجَةٍ:</span> كَضِيقٍ، وَبُعْدٍ، وَخَوْفِ فِتْنَةٍ، وَنَحْوِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ عُدِمَتِ الحَاجَةُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَالصَّحِيحَةُ:</span> مَا بَاشَرَهَا الإِمَامُ، أَوْ أَذِنَ فِيهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنِ اسْتَوَتَا فِي إِذْنٍ أَوْ عَدَمِهِ:</span> فَالسَّابِقَةُ بِالإِحْرَامِ هِيَ الصَّحِيحَةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ جُهِلَ كَيْفَ وَقَعَتَا:</span> صَلَّوْا ظُهْرًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَّ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- قِرَاءَةُ سُورَةِ الكَهْفِ فِي يَوْمِهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>